<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Node.js 게시판</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<div class="container">
			<h1><%=title%></h1>
		</div>
	</header>
	<div class="container">
		<section>
			<div>				
				<table class="table">
					<colgroup>
						<col width="50">
						<col>
						<col width="100">
						<col width="70">
						<col width="160">
					</colgroup>
					<thead>
						<tr>
							<th>번호</th>
							<th>제목</th>
							<th>글쓴이</th>
							<th>조회</th>
							<th>작성일</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
          <% list.forEach(function(article){ %>
            <tr class="active">
							<td><%=article._id%></td>
							<td><a href="/board/<%=article._id%>"><%=article.title%></a></td>
							<td><%=article.writer%></td>
							<td><%=article.view%></td>
							<td><%=article.regdate%></td>
						</tr>
          <% }); %>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
			<hr>
			<div class="form-group text-center">
				<a href="/board/new" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">글쓰기</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
	<footer>
		<div class="container">
			<p class="text-muted">게시판 정책 및 약관 회사소개 광고 마이비즈니스제휴 제안 이용약관 개인정보취급방침 청소년보호 정책 고객센터</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>